{"tid":2478853,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"福斯電動車廣告想酸Subaru不環保　卻忘記自己還在賣燃油車","createTime":"2021-04-07T11:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T02:57:14.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b318d8e3ada34e590a7f6f3acac2c2f3c393cb3","tid":2478853,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"德國車廠福斯（Volkswagen）先前發表了第2款電動車ID.4，該車不僅採用時下最受歡迎的跨界休旅設計，更成為原廠開拓美國、中國電動車市場的全球戰略車款，而ID.4也被外界視為特斯拉（Tesla）Model Y的最大對手；近期福斯釋出了ID.4的宣傳廣告（觀看影片請點此），但內容卻暗酸日本車廠Subaru的車款不環保。<br />\n<br />\n福斯釋出的這段廣告為《Better For Your Family》，影片中段當ID.4行經野外時，乘客正在聆聽大自然的鳥叫聲，此時一輛搭載汽油引擎的休旅車擦身而過，從畫面特寫可見該輛休旅車為SUBARU Outback，車尾還貼了一張「I Love Nature」（我愛大自然）的貼紙；看似無害的片段，其實暗藏了福斯對Subaru的嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZyGcWroz59KU11NKpdqGBaP7BMRUjdJ9oXLxZWDi6tKp?filename=sPGjc7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPGjc7a.jpg&h=507b37b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先，Subaru Outback迎面而來時可清楚聽見其引擎聲，藉此凸顯福斯ID.4無聲的優點，由於燃油引擎會對環境造成汙染，因此車尾的「I Love Nature」（我愛大自然）貼紙也諷刺Subaru根本不愛護環境，另外Subaru Outback的車身相當髒亂，與福斯ID.4的整潔車身形成強烈對比，暗示傳統燃油車與電動車的差異。<br />\n<br />\n儘管這段廣告是在諷刺Subaru不環保，只是福斯好像忘了自己雖然有推出電動車，但目前市售主力仍舊以傳統燃油車款為主，等於廣告也間接酸到自己，只能說這樣「傷敵一千，自損八百」的手法不是太明智啊。"},{"pid":"4b932291c6060ad0778dd886a3400c16f3ea5933","tid":2478853,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X2ynLzoH6H0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX2ynLzoH6H0&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=c52763b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X2ynLzoH6H0</a>"},{"pid":"83898158d936cf02e43f2d0117cbb0552fb33c9c","tid":2478853,"uid":306861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRju6kxue5oy67jYbHiWxbwq7UHx47aBcB8P9bsajfhik?filename=bnOmrst.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnOmrst.gif&h=6ff56e9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"699b24472086186b23aed5b8533fa8588bfddcd5","tid":2478853,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"咁好老實<br />\nSubaru喺環保上嘅effort係傳統車廠中最差嗰批<br />\n到而家都冇一架真正嘅重度hybrid車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜鬼e-boxer得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ee65b4102318b4e40cb2fab36576da46ac132c","tid":2478853,"uid":85405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:35:08.000Z","msg":"小朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f126cd1646055216a59b00c247bb46033d9d5932","tid":2478853,"uid":35045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:36:35.000Z","msg":"Diesel Gate<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f8b11fcd4792cd505778196187130a67feda7d","tid":2478853,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699b24472086186b23aed5b8533fa8588bfddcd5","tid":2478853,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"咁好老實<br />\nSubaru喺環保上嘅effort係傳統車廠中最差嗰批<br />\n到而家都冇一架真正嘅重度hybrid車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜鬼e-boxer得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T00:50:05.000Z","msg":"6個人負皮你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e113dee1be0b02b8300b75e4f64303472401fb","tid":2478853,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f8b11fcd4792cd505778196187130a67feda7d","tid":2478853,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699b24472086186b23aed5